# Deploy on "PUSH" / "push" (KTechnology Solutions)

When the user message is **only** `PUSH`, `push`, or clearly means "deploy now", run without asking for confirmation:

```bash
cd "/Users/kgabrielkaseke/Documents/KTECHNOLOGYSOLUTIONSWEBSITE"
